summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 1 and north 31.25 feet of Lot 2, Block 16, Denny-Fuhrman Addition, and Lot 20, Block 7, Queen Anne Addition; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-253 and 17-200, respectively.
